# Code Owners
# This file defines the default reviewers for different parts of the codebase

# Default reviewers for everything
* @github/team-ops @github/team-devops

# Backend team owns backend-related files
backend/ @github/team-backend
backend/**/*.py @github/team-backend
backend/Dockerfile @github/team-backend
backend/requirements.txt @github/team-backend
backend/package.json @github/team-backend

# Frontend team owns frontend-related files
frontend/ @github/team-frontend
frontend/**/*.js @github/team-frontend
frontend/**/*.jsx @github/team-frontend
frontend/**/*.ts @github/team-frontend
frontend/**/*.tsx @github/team-frontend
frontend/package.json @github/team-frontend

# DevOps owns infrastructure
infra/ @github/team-devops
infra/**/*.tf @github/team-devops
infra/**/*.sh @github/team-devops

# CI/CD configurations
.github/ @github/team-devops
.github/workflows/*.yml @github/team-devops
.github/workflows/*.yaml @github/team-devops
ci/ @github/team-devops
scripts/ @github/team-devops

# Security-related files
**/security* @github/team-security
**/*secret* @github/team-security
**/.env* @github/team-security

# Documentation
*.md docs/ @github/team-docs
docs/** @github/team-docs

# Kubernetes configurations
k8s/ @github/team-devops
*.k8s.yaml @github/team-devops
*.helm.yaml @github/team-devops

# AWS Lambda functions
lambda/ @github/team-backend

# Terraform state and variables (require double approval)
*.tfstate @github/team-devops @github/team-security
*tfvars @github/team-devops @github/team-security

# Database migrations
migrations/ @github/team-backend @github/team-devops
alembic/ @github/team-backend

# Testing
**/*.test.js @github/team-frontend
**/*.test.ts @github/team-frontend
**/*.spec.js @github/team-backend
**/*.spec.ts @github/team-backend
**/pytest.ini @github/team-backend
tests/ @github/team-backend @github/team-frontend

# Configuration files
.config/ @github/team-ops
Makefile @github/team-ops
docker-compose*.yml @github/team-devops